# MyTest.calls downstream

## Inbound Requests

#### POST /api/data → myapp.com

**Request**

```http
POST /api/data HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
Host: myapp.com

{
    "name": "test",
    "value": 42
}
```

**Response**

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "test",
    "value": 42
}
```

## Outbound Requests

#### DELETE /foobar → downstream.example.com

**Request**

```http
DELETE https://downstream.example.com/foobar HTTP/1.1
Host: downstream.example.com
```

**Response**

```http
HTTP/1.1 500 Internal Server Error
Content-Type: text/plain

something went wrong
```
